snippet.title: Challenge of the Tentacle - Trailer [English] Point and Click Adventure Puzzle Game
snippet.description:
Challenge of the Tentacle is a free point and click escape room adventure fangame inspired by Maniac Mansion, Day of the Tentacle and Maniac Mansion Mania. Available now on itch.io
https://amir-matouk.itch.io/challenge-of-the-tentacle
Sorry for the bad quality. I don't know what happened :/
